Petroath: A small but mighty country focusing on industies from the ocean. 
They also have an alliance with Elenath which provides them safety should war break out. 
Their main exports are fish and other seafoods, pearls, and quartz from their mountains. 
The royal family currently consists of Queen Marinth (Centuar) and her consort, Gephe (Halfling), and her son Marcus. 
Marinth herself is a wizard and leads the kingdom by example in making use of magic in all aspects of life. 
Petroath also offers support to the Order of the Dawn and encourages people to send their children there to be trained.
